00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:24,400
 E sad,

450
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,160
 kratke noge,

451
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:26,420
 ovako oni naprave,

452
00:37:26,420 --> 00:37:28,760
